emistry between players. \\>sacking a great new gen coach mid season \\>dressing room controversies. Apart from that, still the highest goal scorrer back to back season. I hope new season, new manager, will bring the great out of our team, vini,mbappe chemistry must be there next season 🫶🏻", 'platform': 'reddit', 'sub_perspective': 3, 'engagement_norm': 0.7062146892655368, 'post_id': '1syp31w', 'created_at': '2026-04-29 05:03:25+00:00'}, {'text': '🚨 CONFIRMED: Real Madrid are talking DIRECTLY to Toni Kroos about hiring him as part of their MANAGEMENT structure. Florentino Perez is PERSONALLY pushing for it.', 'platform': 'twitter', 'sub_perspective': 3, 'engagement_norm': 0.7763157894736842, 'post_id': '2049565669130117241', 'created_at': '2026-04-29 19:05:09+00:00'}] 
