[2026-04-29 17:38:24,220][INFO][social_topic_miner.pipeline]: For Sampled Topic id 5: keyword is ['real', 'madrid', 'role', 'season', 'mourinho', 'couldve', 'talks', 'teams'] and posts are [{'text': "Does Mourinho's Win Rate Make Him Perfect for Real Madrid?", 'platform': 'reddit', 'sub_perspective': 0, 'engagement_norm': 0.388268156424581, 'post_id': '1szc7zu', 'created_at': '2026-04-29 21:27:23+00:00'}, {'text': 'What do you think about Jose Mourinho as manager?', 'platform': 'reddit', 'sub_perspective': 0, 'engagement_norm': 0.6759776536312849, 'post_id': '1syxyww', 'created_at': '2026-04-29 12:53:51+00:00'}, {'text': "🚨 BREAKING: Real Madrid now believe that Jurgen Klopp will ACCEPT THE OFFER to become the club's new COACH!", 'platform': 'twitter', 'sub_perspective': 1, 'engagement_norm': 0.6776315789473685, 'post_id': '2049641004869783592', 'created_at': '2026-04-30 00:04:30+00:00'}, {'text': '🚨 BREAKING: Real Madrid are in talks with Toni Kroos for his RETURN to the club in a new role with KEY responsibilities!', 'platform': 'twitter', 'sub_perspective': 1, 'engagement_norm': 0.8355263157894737, 'post_id': '2049542897880404443', 'created_at': '2026-04-29 17:34:40+00:00'}, {'text': "HERE IT IS : Mbappe 2025/26 Initially, it seems we'll win it all this season. But many blunders cost the whole season. \\>defence crisis \\>poor medical teams \\>too many injuries \\>weak chemistry between players. \\>sacking a great new gen coach mid season \\>dressing room controversies. Apart from that, still the highest goal scorrer back to back season. I hope new season, new manager, will bring the great out of our team, vini,mbappe chemistry must be there next season 🫶🏻", 'platform': 'reddit', 'sub_perspective': 2, 'engagement_norm': 0.6815642458100558, 'post_id': '1syp31w', 'created_at': '2026-04-29 05:03:25+00:00'}, {'text': 'We couldve had it all man Just one transfer. ONE. Even if youre the biggest mbappe glazer, the biggest vini hater, the biggest alonso fan, the biggest ancelotti fan, perez himself whatever, you cant tell you dont sit every once in a while and just ponder on what couldve been if we signed kane when benzema left. In form vini, rodrygo, and jude all playing with kane wouldve been stuff of dreams. He can both score and stat pad and link up perfectly with all his teammates because he has actual good spatial awareness. You never know what wouldve happened since it didnt but i have a strong belief that we couldve went on another threepeat with kane. One transfer couldve sent us beyond the moon and one transfer sent us to the depth of this current hell nonetheless hala madrid', 'platform': 'reddit', 'sub_perspective': 2, 'engagement_norm': 0.664804469273743, 'post_id': '1syjgtb', 'created_at': '2026-04-29 00:40:37+00:00'}, {'text': 'Atp it’s a self repeating cycle. Honestly, Ik many people are against Jose but realistically I don’t see these entitled players respecting anyone else besides these three. And say what you will our periods of success have been with these three. Is Jose possibly washed ? Perhaps, but I say still give him a. Chance. He’s a great manager for drilling the winning mentality into these players and ain’t no one in the squad will have a bigger ego than him.', 'platform': 'reddit', 'sub_perspective': 3, 'engagement_norm': 0.7206703910614525, 'post_id': '1sykb9f', 'created_at': '2026-04-29 01:18:28+00:00'}, {'text': "AMA: The Athletic's Real Madrid reporter, Mario Cortegana Hi everyone! I’m Mario Cortegana, Real Madrid correspondent for The Athletic. I’ve been following the club’s day-to-day since January 2019 in Spain and around the world, and have been fortunate enough to cover their last two Champions League titles and the first Club World Cup ever. I'm delighted to answer your questions for around an hour this Thursday, 30 April, from 5pm BST. Real Madrid news is always fascinating, but I’d say even more so right now, so I look forward to seeing you all here for a good chat! [Mario Cortegana.](", 'platform': 'reddit', 'sub_perspective': 3, 'engagement_norm': 0.44692737430167595, 'post_id': '1szcunh', 'created_at': '2026-04-29 21:52:03+00:00'}] 
