[2026-04-29 17:46:45,053][INFO][social_topic_miner.summarizers.base]: Parse Response from raw strip {
  "category": "Tech",
  "headline": "AI Researchers Develop 'Neuralese' Language for Better Machine Understanding",
  "short_summary": "A group of AI researchers has created a new language called 'neuralese' aimed at improving communication between machines and humans.",
