[2026-04-29 17:51:04,267][INFO][social_topic_miner.pipeline]: For Sampled Topic id 7: keyword is ['musk', 'instagram', 'james', 'comedians', 'dressing', 'openai', 'photo', 'house'] and posts are [{'text': 'Musk v. Altman: A Charm Offensive Gone Astray "OpenAI’s lead attorney, William Savitt, used his opening statements to keep the attention on Musk. This is “a tale of two Elons,” Savitt said. According to the defense, Musk originally pledged far more than the tens of millions that he ultimately gave to OpenAI. He reneged on the pledge, and then in 2018, left in a huff because he wasn’t given the keys to the company, Savitt alleged. It was only after OpenAI became a household name, and Musk’s xAI entered the market, that he became “furious” and decided to sue, Savitt claimed."', 'platform': 'reddit', 'sub_perspective': 0, 'engagement_norm': 0.41388888888888886, 'post_id': '1sz7o8a', 'created_at': '2026-04-29 18:42:14+00:00'}, {'text': 'Andrew Tate Loses His Lawsuit Over Instagram Banning His Accounts', 'platform': 'reddit', 'sub_perspective': 1, 'engagement_norm': 0.8055555555555556, 'post_id': '1sz79gc', 'created_at': '2026-04-29 18:28:08+00:00'}, {'text': 'Streamer Braden “Clavicular” Peters accused of rape and battery in a lawsuit from teen influencer. This article by TMZ summarizes a lawsuit against looksmaxxing influencer Braden Peters accusing him of promising career boosts to a then 16 year old influencer. While she was still underage, Braden transported her to his house where he sexually assaulted her after getting her intoxicated. Braden was a legal adult at the time in 2025. She also accuses him of convincing her he was a doctor and injecting drugs into her face to ‘melt the fat’ against her will.', 'platform': 'reddit', 'sub_perspective': 1, 'engagement_norm': 0.9611111111111111, 'post_id': '1sz7vav', 'created_at': '2026-04-29 18:49:00+00:00'}, {'text': 'Former FBI Director James Comey surrendered to federal authorities today following his indictment over an Instagram photo of seashells spelling out “86 47.” Prosecutors say the post was a threat against President Trump. Comey has denied any violent intent.', 'platform': 'twitter', 'sub_perspective': 2, 'engagement_norm': 0.7236842105263158, 'post_id': '2049552335399960582', 'created_at': '2026-04-29 18:12:10+00:00'}, {'text': 'Former FBI director James Comey has been charged over an Instagram post prosecutors allege threatened Donald Trump’s life. The case centers on a photo of seashells arranged as “8647,” which some interpret as slang for “get rid of 47.” Comey surrendered to law enforcement this', 'platform': 'twitter', 'sub_perspective': 2, 'engagement_norm': 0.9868421052631579, 'post_id': '2049547888750150036', 'created_at': '2026-04-29 17:54:30+00:00'}, {'text': 'Erika Kirk says Candace is directly accusing her of being involved in her husband’s assassination. She’s fed up with the comedy skits mocking her: “I have comedians dressing up in whiteface, I have people saying I’m not fit to be CEO, and I have Candace Owens claiming I murdered my husband.”', 'platform': 'reddit', 'sub_perspective': 3, 'engagement_norm': 0.9944444444444445, 'post_id': '1sza82d', 'created_at': '2026-04-29 20:13:18+00:00'}, {'text': 'Erika Kirk calls out Druski and other impersonators: “Every morning I wake up to a new headline lying about me... I have comedians dressing up in whiteface”', 'platform': 'twitter', 'sub_perspective': 3, 'engagement_norm': 0.9342105263157895, 'post_id': '2049588599797031403', 'created_at': '2026-04-29 20:36:16+00:00'}] 
