den Peters accusing him of promising career boosts to a then 16 year old influencer. While she was still underage, Braden transported her to his house where he sexually assaulted her after getting her intoxicated. Braden was a legal adult at the time in 2025. She also accuses him of convincing her he was a doctor and injecting drugs into her face to ‘melt the fat’ against her will.', 'platform': 'reddit', 'sub_perspective': 2, 'engagement_norm': 0.95625, 'post_id': '1sz7vav', 'created_at': '2026-04-29 18:49:00+00:00'}, {'text': 'Erika Kirk calls out Druski and other impersonators: “Every morning I wake up to a new headline lying about me... I have comedians dressing up in whiteface”', 'platform': 'twitter', 'sub_perspective': 3, 'engagement_norm': 0.9411764705882353, 'post_id': '2049588599797031403', 'created_at': '2026-04-29 20:36:16+00:00'}, {'text': 'Erika Kirk says Candace is directly accusing her of being involved in her husband’s assassination. She’s fed up with the comedy skits mocking her: “I have comedians dressing up in whiteface, I have people saying I’m not fit to be CEO, and I have Candace Owens claiming I murdered my husband.”', 'platform': 'reddit', 'sub_perspective': 3, 'engagement_norm': 0.99375, 'post_id': '1sza82d', 'created_at': '2026-04-29 20:13:18+00:00'}] 
